originalText.text: Dr. Savory is very professional. He listened to my pain issues and  gave me a thorough consultation regarding my neck and back pain. After Dr. Savory gave me  a great adjustment he followed up with some stretches and exercises to alleviate my pain in between appointments. I was recently away for several months and was experiencing awful pain. When i arrived back to NY I  made an appointment and within minutes I felt some relief. I will definitely be continuing to work with Dr. Savory moving forward!

originalText.text: My absolute favorite chiropractor! He is very easy going but always patient in listening/addressing any issues you bring up. He also very carefully checks all your current alignments before doing adjustments and explains everything before and after the adjustments. And afterward my neck and back always feels amazing with so much less stiffness and pain, and much better range of motion. Trust that Dr. Savory will work his magic and fix you!

originalText.text: Dr. Savory is very professional and very thorough with his patients. He has provided the best and most effective treatment for me with personalized stretches and exercises that I can incorporate into my daily routine to help maintain and improve my mobility/back/posture/neck etc. He has even provided me quick adjustments if I am in the area and he has availability. I would consider him one of the best chiropractors in Manhattan, if not the best. I live in Queens but will always make the trek for an appointment with Dr. Savory.
